{"tid":973243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個好開心，心情真係好舒暢嘅經歷","createTime":"2019-01-08T03:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T05:58:48.000Z","uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"050738f40bd8c0b96a46aef9955ccedb438b7899","tid":973243,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:57:52.000Z","msg":"心情好同心情舒暢真係兩回事嚟，姐係失戀嗰種個心屈住屈住嘅感覺同普通唔開心都好唔同<br />\n<br />\n我先，上上下堂，同個女同學傾緊計嘅時候，無啦啦攬埋嚟，果時成個身都好似俾枕頭包圍住咁，好舒服啊，之後個心情真係好舒暢。<br />\n<br />\n不過好耐冇試過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0154aabcc0322dd19695e981824254077c46108","tid":973243,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"成績比預期中好"},{"pid":"041603cf84a6d1f9ac4bd6b6dbc841ea9e8e99b2","tid":973243,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T04:17:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12611368e74c7a8a16105aea5568fe973797ca85","tid":973243,"uid":140574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"食到好食嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}